A digital birthday greeting card that has to be coded first to be seen

<< Sender >>
i   edit the value of the greeting varibale in hb2yencoder.py to jot down the greeting message 
ii  safe
iii run > python3 hb2y.py
iv. Copy value of the greeting message string to text 1, copy value of the picture string to text 2
v.  Send below instructions to the recipient


OUR MISSION SHOULD YOU CHOOSE TO ACCEPT IT IS TO PRINT THE MESSAGE

