0. Use a language of your choice
1. save text1 and text 2 to variables
2. base64 decode text 1 to byte object
3. decode the byte object to utf-8 string
4. reverse the string 
5. save result in variable _m

6. base64 decode text 2 to byte object
7. decode the byte object to utf-8 string
8. save result to variable _p 

9. print _m 
10. print blank line
11. print _p